{"title":"数据结构代码实现：插入类排序","uid":"0039ad01aa5dadb63a86729a9d9754b2","slug":"DataStructure-InsertSort","date":"2020-06-04T12:55:40.000Z","updated":"2020-06-04T14:10:12.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-InsertSort.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200604220955.png","content":"<h2 id=\"直接插入排序\"><a href=\"#直接插入排序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"直接插入排序\"></a>直接插入排序</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>将后面的无序列表依次插入到前面已经排好的有序列表，当要插入的元素小于其前驱，就将前面的有序列表中比他大的元素向后移动一个位置来插入这个数<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200604213438.png\" alt=\"直接插入排序\"></p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">void InsertSort(ElemType A[],int n)&#123;\n    int i,j;\n    for(i&#x3D;2;i&lt;&#x3D;n;i++)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;依次将A[2]~A[n]插入到前面已经排序序列\n        if(A[i]&lt;A[i-1])&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;若A[i]的关键码小于其前驱，需要将A[i]插入有序表\n            A[0]&#x3D;A[i];&#x2F;&#x2F;放到暂存区，A[0]不存放元素\n            for(j&#x3D;i-1;A[0]&lt;A[j];--j)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;从后往前查找待插入的位置\n                A[j+1]&#x3D;A[j];&#x2F;&#x2F;向后挪位\n            &#125;\n            A[j+1]&#x3D;A[0];&#x2F;&#x2F;复制到插入位置\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"折半插入排序\"><a href=\"#折半插入排序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"折半插入排序\"></a>折半插入排序</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>由于插入排序的前面是一个有序列表，所以在查找插入位置的时候可以用折半查找，查找到要插入的位置后，将后面的元素向后移动一个位置来插入该数</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">void MidInsertSort(ElemType A[],int n)&#123;\n    int i,j,low,high,mid;\n    for(i&#x3D;2;i&lt;&#x3D;n;i++)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;依次将A[2]~A[n]插入到前面已经排序序列\n        A[0]&#x3D;A[i];&#x2F;&#x2F;放到暂存区，A[0]不存放元素\n        low&#x3D;1;high&#x3D;i-1;&#x2F;&#x2F;设置折半查找的范围\n        while (low&lt;&#x3D;high)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;折半查找\n            mid&#x3D;(low+high)&#x2F;2;&#x2F;&#x2F;取中间的点\n            if(A[mid]&gt;A[0])&#x2F;&#x2F;查找左半子表\n                high&#x3D;mid-1;\n            else&#x2F;&#x2F;查找右半子表\n                low&#x3D;mid+1;\n        &#125;\n        for(j&#x3D;i-1;j&gt;&#x3D;high;--j)&#123;\n            A[j+1]&#x3D;A[j];&#x2F;&#x2F;统一向后移动元素，空出插入的位置\n        &#125;\n        A[high+1]&#x3D;A[0];&#x2F;&#x2F;插入操作\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"希尔排序\"><a href=\"#希尔排序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"希尔排序\"></a>希尔排序</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>希尔排序就是将数据集分割成若干个小组，然后对每个小组进行插入排序，此时，插入排序所作用的数据量比较小，插入的效率高，<br><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_39207948/article/details/80006224\">希尔排序</a></p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">void ShellSort(ElemType A[],int n)&#123;\n    int dk,i,j;\n    for(dk&#x3D;n&#x2F;2;dk&gt;&#x3D;1;dk&#x3D;dk&#x2F;2)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;步长变化\n        for(i&#x3D;dk;i&lt;&#x3D;n;++i)&#123;\n            if(A[i]&lt;A[i-dk])&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;将A[i]插入有序增量子表\n                A[0]&#x3D;A[i];&#x2F;&#x2F;暂存在A[0]\n                for(j&#x3D;i-dk;j&gt;0&amp;&amp;A[0]&lt;A[j];j&#x3D;j-dk)&#123;\n                    A[j+dk]&#x3D;A[j];&#x2F;&#x2F;记录后移，查找插入的位置\n                &#125;\n                A[j+dk]&#x3D;A[0];&#x2F;&#x2F;插入\n            &#125;\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n","text":"直接插入排序 将后面的无序列表依次插入到前面已经排好的有序列表，当要插入的元素小于其前驱，就将前面的有序列表中比他大的元素向后移动一个位置来插入这个数 void InsertSort(ElemType A[],int n)&#123; int i,j; for(i&#x3D;2;...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/categories/数据结构.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"},{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":11,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"考研","slug":"考研","count":11,"path":"api/tags/考研.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">直接插入排序</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8A%98%E5%8D%8A%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">折半插入排序</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B8%8C%E5%B0%94%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">希尔排序</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"数据结构代码实现：交换类排序","uid":"1fc761e7ae44a5de58caea7dfaaa66ef","slug":"DataStructure-ExchangeSort","date":"2020-06-05T03:41:52.000Z","updated":"2020-06-06T05:25:04.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-ExchangeSort.json","keywords":null,"cov